# CODEOWNERS — security review routing for Macena CS2 Analyzer
#
# Doctrine: every PR that touches a security-critical path requires review by the
# repository owner before merge. The threat-model-gate workflow labels matching PRs
# `security-review-required` and links to SECURITY/THREAT_MODEL.md.
#
# References:
# - SECURITY/BOUNDARY_FILES.txt — canonical trust-boundary file inventory
# - SECURITY/THREAT_MODEL.md    — threat model that must be updated for boundary changes
# - SECURITY/CONTROL_CATALOG.md — controls mapped to NIST SSDF / OWASP ASVS / CWE

